{"tid":1058830,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"月薪2萬被老闆半夜狂操　女星停經2年險沒命","createTime":"2019-03-12T20:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T08:58:53.000Z","uid":10806,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a50b95506df4aa2fe3cdb8765fd64af653f692","tid":1058830,"uid":10806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T20:43:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://shareba.com/read-blog/52001ibjm5vt7h09317gn75k783608?fbclid=IwAR17GuTx05g95pKft3cVm5jDv_SlSYwTne6_OsTBCpFqtUDJ2zOF5y7rP7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshareba.com%2Fread-blog%2F52001ibjm5vt7h09317gn75k783608%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17GuTx05g95pKft3cVm5jDv_SlSYwTne6_OsTBCpFqtUDJ2zOF5y7rP7s&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=2fb0d179\" target=\"_blank\">https://shareba.com/read-blog/52001ibjm5vt7h09317gn75k783608?fbclid=IwAR17GuTx05g95pKft3cVm5jDv_SlSYwTne6_OsTBCpFqtUDJ2zOF5y7rP7s</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dzvVOY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dzvVOY.png&h=8b73af06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAp0yA1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAp0yA1.png&h=d9e797f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gDMt9n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gDMt9n.png&h=7f3192ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n27歲歌手高以馨近日上節目，分享自己的離家經驗，她表示一上大學媽媽要她搬出去，也同時斷了金援，為了養活自己只好兼了4份工，曾半夜被老闆狂call，為了2萬元的薪水搞壞身體。<br />\n<br />\n高以馨媽媽為了訓練她獨立，上大學便搬出家裡，為了養活自己高以馨即使課業繁忙，還是兼了4份工作，包括網拍、家教、補習班老師以及工地繪圖，其中工地的老闆，竟在半夜要她交出平面圖，並要求在早上6點前交差，她時常拚命趕工，結果為了工地的2萬月薪，差點賠上性命。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣啲標題真係CLS<br />\n我以為2萬包隻私家雞，個老細屌到佢停經同差啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8ca22cda5a95671df46a29ae0a5afbf3635c74da","tid":1058830,"uid":17232,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T23:13:58.000Z","msg":"停經邊到講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif